  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Consultant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are seeking a motivated <strong>Consultant</strong> to provide professional guidance and support to clients while assisting in project coordination and business operations. This role is suitable for individuals who are proactive, analytical, and enjoy interacting with clients to solve problems.</p><p>No prior experience is required, as training and mentorship will be provided.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist clients with business inquiries and project-related tasks</p></li><li><p>Support senior consultants in planning and executing projects</p></li><li><p>Conduct research, prepare reports, and analyse data for client solutions</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams to ensure smooth project delivery</p></li><li><p>Participate in client meetings and follow up on action items</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate records and documentation of client interactions</p></li><li><p>Support business development and operational initiatives as needed</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Good command of English, both written and spoken</p></li><li><p>Strong communication, problem-solving, and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Organised, responsible, and able to manage multiple tasks</p></li><li><p>Comfortable using email, spreadsheets, and basic office tools</p></li><li><p>Prior consulting experience is a plus but not required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Monthly salary <strong>SGD 2,650 – 3,050</strong></p></li><li><p>On-the-job training and mentorship</p></li><li><p>Exposure to client management, business projects, and consulting workflows</p></li><li><p>Supportive and collaborative team environment</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for career growth within the consulting domain</p></li></ul>",
